<PageTitle>Collapse</PageTitle>
<h2>Collapse</h2>
<p>Use <code>Collapse</code> to conditionally show or hide your content. The hidden part stays rendered in the DOM tree.</p>

<h4>Example</h4>
<p>Surround your elements with <code>Collapse</code> and set <code>Active</code> to your desired value.</p>
<div class="collapse-example">
    <button @onclick="() => Expanded = !Expanded">Toggle active</button>
    <Collapse Active="Expanded">
        @* TODO create spacer component *@
